      "rationale": "A parameter equivalency table was prepared documenting 18 FEA input parameters and their experimental counterparts, including screw geometry, rod geometry, material properties, block spacing, fixture boundary conditions, and loading rate. All 18 parameters were sourced from direct measurement or certified material data; none required assumed values without experimental basis. Boundary condition equivalency was verified by comparing measured fixture compliance against the rigid-boundary FEA assumption, finding < 1.5% influence on stiffness QoI. Gradation 3 achieved and required."
